description.text: Newly constructed town home in Mid-City, minutes from Culver City, Beverly Hills, Metro lines and the beaches of Santa Monica and Marina Del Rey. This home was just completed and includes high-end finishes. The main floor has a full kitchen with marble counter tops, stainless steel appliances and laundry hookups. The bathrooms are updated with stone counter tops. The master bedroom has a walk-in closet and private bathroom with floor to ceiling marble counter tops. A private two car garage is accessed from the gated driveway. This home is protected by a security camera system. Come take a look today!

Stunning new and modern 4-bedroom, 4.5-bathroom townhouse, designed as a luxury single family home. This light and bright unit boasts 10' ceilings, a desirable open floor plan, and many designer finishes. Features include a rooftop deck with built-in BBQ, dedicated 2-car garage, gourmet kitchen with breakfast bar, wide plank white oak flooring, white quartz kitchen counters with new Samsung appliances, in-unit washer & dryer, recessed lighting and in-ceiling speakers. The spacious primary bedroom includes a custom walk-in closet, and deep soaking tubs/shower. The expansive rooftop provides incredible views and is the perfect space to entertain. Please inquire today!

Welcome to the pinnacle of luxury living in Culver City as a resident of The Penthouse Collection at ARQ located at the exclusive Cumulus District in West L.A. This stunning penthouse residence features 2 bedroom and 2 bathrooms and is built with the highest quality and standard among all penthouse residences in Los Angeles. Penthouse 3 features 9 foot ceilings with floor-to-ceiling windows, a private terrace with unobstructed, panoramic views of L.A. from the Hollywood Hills all the way to the Pacific ocean, Italian-style cabinetry, quartz countertops, a wet bar, and comes fully equipped with Bosch stainless steel appliances. The unparalleled Amenities at ARQ include a Jr. Olympic-size pool, fitness center, office spaces, rooftop terrace and spa, as well as a sky lounge complete with a rooftop spa and indoor lounge. Village Green is a National Historical Landmark. This spacious top-floor unit with 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom offers a lots of natural light and views of gorgeous trees and a lush green landscape from the living room and a bedroom. Private patio, large walk in closet next to stairs, beautiful wood bookcase that you can decorate in your own style, nice size dining/living room, and two great sized bedrooms. Laundry is in the community, one car garage, guest parking (you can park), and 24-HR security. Landlord covers water and trash. The Green has walking paths, well-kept trees, and acres of grass. Centrally located near the Expo train, Crenshaw Plaza, shopping, restaurants, Culver City, West Side, and Downtown LA. THIS UNIT IS A MUST SEE!

Beautiful views abound in this spacious remodeled top floor unit in iconic Village Green, a National Historic Landmark set on 68 acres of parkland offering 1, 500+ mature trees, extensive walking paths, 24/7 patrolled security, and summer jazz concerts and movie nights. This two bedroom/one bath condo features stunning hardwood floors, fireplace, balcony, enclosed patio with lemon tree, eat-in kitchen with granite counters and stainless appliances, lots of storage, and verdant views from every room - you'll feel like you're living in a mid-century treehouse! Minutes to the 10, Expo line, downtown Culver City and brand new Cumulus complex. Includes 2 off-street parking spaces (one space in private garage) plus ample guest parking. Live in the middle of Los Angeles, yet get away from it all at Village Green.

Welcome to 5335 Homeside Ave, a stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom townhome in the heart of Los Angeles, CA (West Adams). This modern townhome offers a spacious open-concept floor plan and boasts modern upgrades throughout. The inviting living area is filled with natural light, creating a warm ambiance. The sleek kitchen features stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and stylish countertops. Adjacent to the kitchen is a dining area perfect for hosting meals or casual gatherings. Upstairs, you'll find four generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite. This townhome also provides convenient 3 parking spaces - 1 covered and 2 uncovered, ensuring you always have a place to park. Situated in a desirable neighborhood, this townhome offers easy access to a wide range of amenities, including dining, shopping, and entertainment options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to lease this modern 4-bedroom townhome at 5335 Homeside Ave. Schedule a viewing today and make it your new home in Los Angeles! Tenant Pays All Utilities.

description.text: Welcome home to this cute, updated 1920s Spanish Casita with beautiful fenced front yard in blossoming West Adams! A fully detached 2 bedroom plus bonus room house with no shared walls and no one above or below, this is the front unit of a small triplex. Adorable arched front atrium porch leads into a main living area featuring plenty of natural light and character elements: a decorative fireplace flanked by built-in storage cabinets and charming arched partitions that reveal an updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances. Two bedrooms are connected by a Jack & Jill bathroom that has new floor tiles, a new toilet, new mirrored medicine cabinet, new space-saving sink, freshly reglazed bath tub, and new multi-function shower head. Bonus room with additional ensuite three-quarter bathroom features a stackable laundry unit and would make an ideal office, laundry room, yoga room, or possible small third bedroom. Newly installed HVAC unit provides central heat and air conditioning controlled by a Nest thermostat. Enjoy the outdoors in the lush front yard surrounded by bougainvillea, fire stick plant, and passionfruit vines embracing a private perimeter fence. Comes with a single-car garage for parking and/or storage, and an optional second uncovered off-street parking spot. Near West Adams hot spots Highly Likely Cafe, Party Beer Company Brewery, Cento, Alta, Adams Wine Shop, Vicky's All Day, and so much more. Less than 2 miles from the LaCienega Whole Foods Market which just opened last year. Enjoy all this super-central location has to offer!

This charmer has been tastefully restored & updated for modern-day living while maintaining original 1920s details. It sits behind a long front yard modern fence, Step into this luxurious home & be swept away. You'll forget where you are. This well-orchestrated 1, 120 sq ft layout, encompasses 3 beds & 1 full bath. Features include an oversize backyard perfect for entertaining, remodeled kitchen, & bath, and wood flooring thru out. The home has gone through extensive restoration w/ s/s appliances. Tastefully designed by Shiela Nassir Interiors. Long driveway for multiple car parking, in addition to R V parking. West Adams Area w/ many close-by restaurants, markets, & art galleries. Blocks to the Expo Line. Minutes to Downtown Culver City, easy freeway access & direct routes to Hollywood, Santa Monica, Downtown, & LAX. Pets are welcome. Price is based on 1 yr lease.

Totally Renovated Modern Gated 2 Story Duplex With 2 Bedrooms and 1 Baths each. Kitchen with Shaker White Cabinets and Ceasarstone Countertops, Dishwasher and Stainless Steel Appliances. Upper Unit with Balcony off the Living-room. Large Closets with Glass Panel Doors, Bathrooms with Lighted Bluetooth Mirrors. Off Street Parking, Close to Metro Link, Shopping and Public Transportation.
